query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 100 AND q.view_count <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('adapter',
'android-alertdialog',
'arguments',
'generator',
'imap',
'installation',
'ionic3',
'paperclip',
'sdl',
'uiimagepickercontroller',
'visual-studio-2012');
